      "body" : "@2cupsOfTech On 2nd thought, that’s good advice. Currently both tests are the same at runtime because <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Thread.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thread</a> does not override <code>equals</code>, and so falls back to <code>==</code>, but that could change in future. So I corrected the answer."
