    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>You can check</strong> </p>\n\n<pre><code>if(Looper.myLooper() == Looper.getMainLooper()) {\n   // You are on mainThread \n}else{\n// you are on non-ui thread\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
