    "question_id" : 11411022,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>Xamarin.Android</code> port: (<em><code>C#</code></em>)</p>\n\n<pre><code>public bool IsMainThread =&gt; Build.VERSION.SdkInt &gt;= BuildVersionCodes.M\n    ? Looper.MainLooper.IsCurrentThread\n    : Looper.MyLooper() == Looper.MainLooper;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (IsMainThread) {\n    // you are on UI/Main thread\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
