    "question_id" : 11411022,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>So another answer to join the company, for some extension file in kotlin:</p>\n<pre><code>import android.os.Looper.getMainLooper\nimport java.lang.Thread.currentThread\n\nval Thread.isMain get() = getMainLooper().thread == this\n\nval isThreadMain get() = getMainLooper().thread == currentThread()\n</code></pre>\n"
